  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "NVwRxCbBnr+bkB4T8Iv8OMwyMnY=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:37.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# model-editor wiring\n\nThe integration layer between document models and their editors.\n\n## Core Wiring Pattern\n- [[editors use the modern React hooks pattern from reactor-browser]] \u2014 the useSelectedXDocument pattern\n- [[editors import action creators from gen/creators not from model source]] \u2014 correct import path for creators\n- [[generateId from document-model/core provides deterministic IDs for dispatch]] \u2014 ID generation before dispatch\n- [[useSelectedDocument hook is auto-generated per document model]] \u2014 auto-generated hooks per model\n\n## Drive-Level Wiring\n- [[apps use useSelectedDrive to access drive state and filter nodes]] \u2014 drive editors filter nodes by type\n\n## By Editor\n- [[service-offering editor wires four tab views to the service-offering model]] \u2014 ResourceTemplateSelector, ServiceCatalog, TierDefinition, TheMatrix\n- [[subscription-instance editor provides client and operator views with billing]] \u2014 dual-mode with ImportServiceConfigButton bridge to ServiceOffering\n- [[resource-template editor manages template info and facet targeting]] \u2014 simplest editor, two components\n- [[resource-instance editor manages provisioning lifecycle and facet configuration]] \u2014 most action creator imports (17), lifecycle state machine\n\n## By Document Model\n\n| Model | Editor | Hook | Modules Used |\n|-------|--------|------|--------------|\n| service-offering | service-offering-editor | useSelectedServiceOfferingDocument | offering, services, tiers, option-groups, service-groups, configuration |\n| subscription-instance | subscription-instance-editor | useSelectedSubscriptionInstanceDocument | subscription, service, service-group, metrics, customer |\n| resource-template | resource-template-editor | useSelectedResourceTemplateDocument | template-management, facet-targeting |\n| resource-instance | resource-instance-editor | useSelectedResourceInstanceDocument | instance-management, configuration-management |\n| facet | (no dedicated editor) | useFacetDocument | \u2014 |\n\n## Cross-Model Editors\n- [[subscription-instance editor provides client and operator views with billing]] \u2014 imports from ServiceOffering via mapOfferingToSubscription\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[index]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:37.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:37.000Z"
    }
  },
